sentences.english: Why not have the Ivory Coast as the first African team in the Final?
sentences.chinese: 科特迪瓦爲什麼不能是第一個闖進決賽圈的球隊呢？

sentences.english: Gbagbo thanked China for its long-term selfless assistance to Cote d'Ivoire.
sentences.chinese: 巴博感謝中國長期以來給予科特迪瓦的無私援助。

sentences.english: This marks an escalation for the UN mission in Ivory Coast.
sentences.chinese: 這表明聯合國在科特迪瓦任務的升級。

sentences.english: Western Ivory Coast has also seen vicious battles between rival militias.
sentences.chinese: 科特迪瓦西部之間也出現惡性競爭的民兵作戰。

sentences.english: The case was detected by cross-border investigation of the outbreak in Côte d'Ivoire.
sentences.chinese: 該病例是在對科特迪瓦的疫情進行跨境調查時發現的。

sentences.english: Sylvain Côté is Artistic Technical Director at Artificial Mind & Movement.
sentences.chinese: 西爾萬科特迪瓦是人工的藝術思維及技術總監運動。

sentences.english: Emmanuel Ebouehas been named in Ivory Coast's provisional 30-man squad.
sentences.chinese: 埃布埃被選入科特迪瓦隊的30人名單。

sentences.english: The Ivorians' next fixture is against Libya on Tuesday.
sentences.chinese: 科特迪瓦將在週二迎戰下一個對手利比亞。

sentences.english: That is a firm stance Cote d'Ivoire will never change.
sentences.chinese: 這是科特迪瓦永遠也不會改變的堅定立場。

sentences.english: Cote d'Ivoire staunchly supports China's reunification cause.
sentences.chinese: 科特迪瓦堅定地支持中國的統一大業。

sentences.english: Kalou will now join older brother Bonaventure as an Ivorian international.
sentences.chinese: 卡勞將和他的哥哥一樣作爲科特迪瓦國家隊成員。
